videos.headline: Citadel coach collapses on sideline, helped off the court
videos.description: Citadel basketball coach Duggar Baucom collapses on the sideline versus Duke and is helped off the court.

videos.headline: Paolo Banchero leads Duke to a big win over Citadel
videos.description: Paolo Banchero posts 31 points, 8 rebounds and 4 assists in Duke's 107-81 win over Citadel.
